<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="<%=require('assets/misc/favicon.png')%>" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spartan:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Frontend Mentor | Social Proof Section</title>
  </head>
  <body class="h-full flex justify-center text-sm text-neutral">
    <main class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 w-10/12 max-w-6xl min-h-screen gap-y-16 py-16 font-primary text-center">
      <div class="lg:text-left lg:w-5/6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">10,000+ of our users love our products.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
          We only provide great products combined with excellent customer service. See what our satisfied customers are saying about our
          services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row lg:flex-col xl:items-center gap-6 justify-around text-center font-bold text-primary">
        <li
          class="
            rating__cat
            flex flex-col
            lg:flex-row
            xl:self-start
            gap-y-3
            lg:gap-x-5
            bg-neutral-light
            rounded-xl
            py-0.5
            px-8
            items-center
            lg:pr-24
            flex-grow
          "
        >
          <p>Rated 5 Stars in Reviews</p>
        </li>
        <li
          class="
            rating__cat
